Office install on RDS server witch all users can use normaly. Please intall besore Office Deplyment tool
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=49117

In my case i use 32 bit.



Script
<Configuration>
  <Add OfficeClientEdition="32" Version="16.0.16130.20332" >  // оффис версия для 12р 
    <Product ID="O365ProPlusRetail">
      <Language ID="en-us" />
    </Product>
  </Add>  
<Property Name="SharedComputerLicensing" Value="1" />
</Configuration>
